# Release Version Bumps

Before any publish or release task for this repository:

- Bump the package version instead of reusing the previous release version.
- Keep version strings in sync across `pyproject.toml`, `flex_mls/__init__.py`, and `flex_mls/base_client.py`.
- Make sure the release tag matches the package version in `vX.Y.Z` format.
- Do not consider a publish task complete until the version bump is included in the same change.

Example:

- If the next release is `0.1.1`, update all version references to `0.1.1` and publish from tag `v0.1.1`.
